div.p: The IPPD team groups its service offerings according to the interaction modes defined by the Team Topologies model:

ul.li: Collaboration: working together for a defined period of time to discover new things (APIs, practices, technologies, etc.)
X-as-a-Service: one team provides and one team consumes something “as a Service”k
Facilitation: one team helps and mentors another team

div.p: Following this model allows for clear interactions between IPPD and other teams.
